data.description: Explore this stunning 5-bedroom, 2.5-bathroom residence in Lemoore, Ca. Boasting a spacious backyard with a sizable pool. Upon entering, you are welcomed by vaulted ceilings, a fireplace, and exposed brick accents. The generously sized kitchen offers ample cabinet space and elegant granite countertops. The backyard is an entertainer's delight, featuring a large pool for family enjoyment, a deck for grilling and socializing, and plenty of space for outdoor activities. Don't miss the chance to schedule your showing now.
